<paragraph id="94C2F536F0749465BEB4E004FC145E49" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
China, India, Bangladesh, Nepal, Pakistan (
<bibRefCitation id="37B694A0D3EA487CC68958E795ACA55E" author="Cigliano, MM" journalOrPublisher="The Zoological Survey of India, Calcutta" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" publicationUrl="http://Orthoptera.SpeciesFile.org" refId="B6" refString="Cigliano, MM, Braun, H, Eades, DC, Otte, D, 2020. Orthoptera species file online, version 5.0/5.0. http://Orthoptera.SpeciesFile.org" title="Orthoptera species file online, version 5.0 / 5.0." url="http://Orthoptera.SpeciesFile.org" year="2020">Cigliano et al. 2020</bibRefCitation>
