<subSubSection id="4F3DC18F5072DB765251BC71E0006626" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="9A82917D8F480C9805341305ED1F7827" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="3B204348B565D2F2CA9258450686ECB3" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
This species was erected by 
<bibRefCitation id="1C6A0DAD33AF3F134F11FFD847876E53" author="Saeed, A" journalOrPublisher="International Journal of Agriculture and Biology" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="175 - 182" refId="B25" refString="Saeed, A, 2000. New species and Records of some Crickets (Gryllinae: Gryllidae: Orthoptera) from Pakistan. International Journal of Agriculture and Biology 2 (3): 175 - 182" title="New species and Records of some Crickets (Gryllinae: Gryllidae: Orthoptera) from Pakistan." volume="2" year="2000">Saeed (2000)</bibRefCitation>
from Peshawar, KPK based on a single female specimen; subsequently 
<bibRefCitation id="E18E8FBEE606E6CCEA95D7FC5E3386AB" author="Malik, S" journalOrPublisher="Sindh University Research Journal (Science Series)" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="289 - 290" refId="B17" refString="Malik, S, Soomro, NM, Baloach, TJN, Wagan, MS, 2013. A new species of genus Callogryllus Sjostedt (Gryllidae: Orthoptera) from Sindh, Pakistan. Sindh University Research Journal (Science Series) 45 (2): 289 - 290" title="A new species of genus Callogryllus Sjostedt (Gryllidae: Orthoptera) from Sindh, Pakistan." volume="45" year="2013">Malik et al. (2013)</bibRefCitation>
reported its male from the Hyderabad -Sindh. We have a single female from the rocky area of Nagarparkar and confirm its presence in the desert area.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
